Stefan Jochum, a spokesman for the 
Lech ski area where the accident occurred, said the incident took place 
this afternoon as the prince and other skiers were on slopes away from
the marked Lech ski runs.

The trails were laden with snow after weeks of record 
falls.

Mr Jochum said: 'A snow slide came down and the 
prince was buried as the only member of the group.'

