He could not confirm the news report that the prince had been buried for 
15 minutes before he was found and said he had no information on the 
nature of his injuries.

Members of the royal family are skiing in the mountain village of Lech, which has been hit by heavy snowfall in recent days.

Friso was in Lech along with other members of the royal family.

The second of Beatrix's three sons, Friso gave up any claim to the 
Dutch throne in order to marry Dutch commoner Mabel Wisse Smit, in 2004. The pair have two daughters, Emma and Joanna.

